overview: The traditional Finnish sport "Mölkky" is divided into 3 teams to play against each other! The team that won the "Mölkky" will have the privilege of having fun at the barbecue that will be held later! And after a long time! Morning Musume.'21 The annual barbecue tournament! !! Bake meat at a chartered campsite! eat! !! Talk! !! !! After the barbecue, at the end of summer, Morning Musume.'21 gets excited with fireworks.Following Vol.136, Morning Musume.'21 on location for the first time in a long time. Enjoy the DVD MAGAZINE! !! ("Sato Masaki" who could not participate in the location participates in the narration.)
title: Morning Musume.'21 DVD Magazine Vol.137
